ke mistakes. Simply put, if you have never made a mistake in your life, then thatmeans that you have never taken a risk. Taking risks means that you go outside ofyour comfort zone – that you go outside of your boundaries. The most successful people are the ones who are not afraid to give it their all and possibly humiliate themselves greatly in front of others. It’s like that one saying, ‘The personwho asks a question is a fool for five minutes, but the person who never asks and remains silent is a fool forever.’ You choose the way you want to live your life.', 61541, 0), (389539, 'Because I know the things I should be able to accomplish, and I don''t want to do so.', 34, 0), (389540, 'The only thing that''s ours to accept is the fact that we don''t always get to know the answers.', 312, 0), (389541, 'We always hurt the ones we love, darling. You’ll have to tell her you’re sorry. And mean it and give her time. - Grace Trevelyan-Grey to Christian Grey', 177, 0), (389542, 'The world''s most sensible and the most idiotic person lies within us..the worst part is we can''t say who is who', 936, 0), (389543, 'Philosophy lives in words, but truth and fact well up into our lives in ways that exceed verbal formulation.', 1782, 0), (389544, 'A mask does not hide who you are, it shows exactly what you want others to see.', 25393, 0), (389545, 'If you start out by promising what you don''t even have yet, you''ll lose your desire to work toward getting it.', 34, 0), (389546, 'So when modern-day religious conservatives wax nostalgic about how marriage is a sacred tradition that reaches back into history for thousands of uninterrupted years, they are absolutely correct, but in only one respect—only if they happen to be talking about Judaism.', 20, 0), (389547, 'if lying would be a crime, we would all be in jail right now', 61542, 0), (389548, 'You are the books you read!!!', 61543, 0), (389549, 'Be kind to one another and seek beauty in all you do.', 7223, 0), (389550, 'No politic